nodes.text: Supreme Commander of the Corellian Defense Force

Supreme Commander of the Corellian Defense Force was the position given to Wedge Antilles after the death of Minister of War Thrackan Sal-Solo. It made him the highest ranking officer of the Corellian defense fleet. After Antilles resigned, the post was given to Genna Delpin. If Delpin remained the Supreme Commander, or the post remained in existence after Turr Phennir was appointed Supreme Commander of the Confederation military remains unknown.
